<BR><BR>

<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="verdana, arial">

<B>Power of the Orb</B> (Sub-quest)<BR>

<P>This quest is given by Rykas in Lake Rathtear and it is needed to as part of the <B>Element of Fire</B> main quest above. Rykas needs three items to complete this quest. Each item is another quest in itself as follows...</P><BR><BR> 

1. Power of the Elements<BR>
2. Words of Magi`Kot<BR>
3. Words of Mastery<BR><BR>
</FONT>

